Version info:

Version 0.9 Beta
This version of Pacman is not yet complete. Expect semi-regular
updates.

The following features are not implemented at all:

-   End of game. ( The game loops )
-   Extra game mode.
-   High score.
-   Levels on disk.
-   Intro sequence.

The following features are only partially implemented:

-   Different difficulty levels / multiple speeds.
-   Loading different gfx/sound 'sets'.
-   There is only 1 level. Levels are currently hard coded and can 
    only be changed by editing the source code.

The Following bugs are known:

-  The ghosts do not act properly when moving through the tunnel.
-  Pacman does not immediatly pick up the dot he is positioned 
   over when a new level starts.
-  When choosing difficulty level, the text is sometimes misformed.

For further version info see history.txt. All changes are
recorded there.


