Installing Pacman:

Installing Pacman is simple: just copy all the files to a
directory on your harddisk. The easiest way to do this is by just
dragging the disk icon onto your harddisk. A directory Pacman
will then be made automatically.


File info:

To avoid virus infection, The executable sizes will now be given:

Main executable:   Pacman  - 89656 Bytes.


